title: koffee_with_karan_kareena_and_ranbir.mkv
description:
It's the Kapoors on Koffee With Karan S4! Karan brings the cousins, Ranbir Kapoor and Kareena Kapoor together for the very first time. If you missed the episode on television, fret not, we've got it right here! Sure to keep you hooked as Ranbir speaks about Katrina! Kareena speaks about some "rumours" about Ranbir that never made it in the media!
